OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry morning with
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny spells. Turning
OL,7,Fcloudier in the afternoon as a band of
OL,8,Frain spreads eastwards, accompanied by
OL,9,Fstrengthening southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain. Rain clearing to
OL,13,Fthe east overnight with a few showers
OL,14,Flingering and some clearer spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping. Winds strong this evening
OL,16,Fthen easing overnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FA mixed day with some bright
OL,19,Fand sunny spells but also blustery
OL,20,Fshowers feeding in from the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
